### Exercise Slide

```jsx
<Slide backgroundColor="#1A1A2E">
  <FlexBox flexDirection="column" alignItems="center" justifyContent="center" height="100%">
    <Text fontSize="24px" color="#E94560" fontWeight="bold">EXERCISE</Text>
    <Heading fontSize="h2" color="white" margin="20px 0">
      [Exercise Title]
    </Heading>
    <Box backgroundColor="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" padding={30} borderRadius={8} width="80%">
      <OrderedList>
        <ListItem color="white">Open <code>exercises/[number]/start.js</code></ListItem>
        <ListItem color="white">[Specific task 1]</ListItem>
        <ListItem color="white">[Specific task 2]</ListItem>
        <ListItem color="white">Run <code>npm test exercises/[number]</code> to verify</ListItem>
      </OrderedList>
    </Box>
    <Text fontSize="28px" color="#E94560" marginTop={30} fontWeight="bold">
      Time: 15 minutes
    </Text>
  </FlexBox>
  <Notes>
    Set a visible timer. Walk around the room. Common sticking points:
    - [Thing 1 people get wrong]
    - [Thing 2 people forget]
    If someone finishes early, point them to the bonus challenge in
    exercises/[number]/bonus.js
  </Notes>
</Slide>
```

