---

### Group Review Slide

```jsx
<Slide>
  <Heading>Exercise Review</Heading>
  <Text>Let's walk through the solution together.</Text>
  <CodePane language="javascript" highlightRanges={[[1, 3], [5, 8], [10, 12]]}>
{`// Solution code here
// Step through the approach
// Highlight the key decisions`}
  </CodePane>
  <Notes>
    Ask: "Who wants to share their approach?" Let 1-2 people explain
    their solution before showing yours. Validate different approaches.
    "That works too, and here is why I prefer this pattern: [reason]."
  </Notes>
</Slide>
```

