## Workshop Pacing Guide

| Duration | Sections | Exercises | Breaks |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 hour | 2 | 2 | 0 |
| 2 hours | 3-4 | 3-4 | 1 (10 min) |
| Half day (3h) | 4-5 | 4-5 | 2 (15 min) |
| Full day (6h) | 6-8 | 6-8 | 3 + lunch |

---

## Usage

1. Create React project with Spectacle (see `frameworks/spectacle.md`).
2. Build slide components using patterns above.
3. Create `exercises/` directory with numbered exercise folders.
4. Each exercise folder: `start.js` (skeleton), `solution.js` (answer), `test.js` (verification).
5. Apply brand theme via the theme object.
6. Test presenter mode (`Alt + P`).
